        <title type="html"><![CDATA[首发 M4 芯片，苹果正准备将 iPad 进化为“Ai Pad”]]></title>
        <id>2247564729_1</id>
        <link href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNjU2ODM2NQ==&amp;mid=2247564729&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=6a14989694c7f82cb54b1347a373cb3b&amp;chksm=c236e77bf5416e6d275512f8d868b7a37ad525bca58988e03202a831fd7232f3dc8cfc18e7f3#rd"/>
        <updated>2024-05-08T01:39:32.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;" data-mpa-powered-by="yiban.io"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="562" data-backw="562" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100081058" data-ratio="1" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBJptz9zWxHxcOPokqmxTT1YNalQIkkWeY1SGkaaIkCqsoRTzarKYYnnzp8sNhh0qp77cm3WE82XIQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><div style="margin-bottom: 30px;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-image: none;background-position: initial;background-size: initial;background-repeat: initial;background-attachment: initial;background-origin: initial;background-clip: initial;"><p style="padding-top: 15px;letter-spacing: inherit;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);font-size: 13px;line-height: 21px;">作者<span style="letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(221, 221, 221);">｜</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">陆</span><br style="letter-spacing: inherit;">邮箱<span style="letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(221, 221, 221);">｜</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">xiaoyu@pingwest.com</span></p></div><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">在今晚的新品发布会上，苹果对 iPad 系列产品线进行了“史诗级”更新，iPad Pro系列更是破天荒的跳过了 M3 芯片，直接首发搭载了性能更加强劲的 M4 芯片。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">苹果在今晚的发布会上表示，这款 M4 芯片的性能已经超越了市面上的所有 AI PC。但令人遗憾的是，今晚的发布会上，苹果并没有针对 AI 方面有过多的演示，<span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">只是表示全新的 M4 芯片可以为各种 AI 任务提速，并且将 iPad OS 的机器学习推上新维度，但这也是苹果首次在手持设备上提及 AI 特性。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">配件方面，Apple Pencil 和妙控键盘配件也迎来了更新，让我们一起来看看。</p><div style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div style="letter-spacing: inherit;"><p style="margin-bottom: -30px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;">1</p></div><p style="margin-left: 15px;padding-bottom: 24px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 20px;color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;font-weight: bold;"><strong style="letter-spacing: inherit;color: rgb(55, 80, 114);">iPad Air 11/13寸</strong></p></div><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">在意识到用户对大屏 iPad 的需求之后，苹果在今晚果断的推出了相较于12.9寸 iPad Pro 而言，更加具有“性价比”的13寸 iPad Air。</p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="357" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="100081043" data-ratio="0.6346666666666667" data-type="png" data-w="750" height="1584" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 100%;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto;" title="图源：苹果" width="2494" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBJptz9zWxHxcOPokqmxTT1YIKkOoCatKWxbw25wXRZUTAMmFicnwxAibUNozzxyXVcuVX9nKD3gvdzA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"><figcaption style="margin-top: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">图源：苹果</figcaption></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">13寸 iPad Air 的屏幕可用面积比11寸增加了30%，用户可以在同屏下显示更多的功能信息。11寸和13寸的 iPad Air 屏幕均采用 Liquid视网膜屏，依旧不支持可变刷新率。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">新款iPad Air 用上了 M2芯片，所以也就“理所应当”的支持了 Apple Pencil 的悬停预览功能。并且，全新设计的iPad Air 11/13寸将前置摄像头横向放在中间，可以在用户拨打 FaceTime 或使用其他视频软件时始终让用户的面部处于屏幕中心区域（支持自动跟踪）。</p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="333" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="100081041" data-ratio="0.5933333333333334" data-type="png" data-w="750" height="1318" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 100%;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto;" title="图源：苹果" width="2220" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBJptz9zWxHxcOPokqmxTT1Y5h8qr9iaRhgkgjHibBgz8eCOdj5WicmPpkic5nibxv3w47bveOLFc6ZFZtw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"><figcaption style="margin-top: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">图源：苹果</figcaption></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">同时新款的iPad Air增加了横向立体声扬声器和空间音频，我想今晚之后，13寸的 iPad Air 应该是目前 iPad 产品线中最适合“买后爱奇艺”的一款产品。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">新 iPad Air 的起步容量为128G，共有128G/256G/512G/1TB四个容量，11寸的售价分别为4799、5599、7299、8999元不等，13寸的售价为6499、7299、8999、10699元不等。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">5G蜂窝版本在此售价的基础上再增加1000元。</span></p><div style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div style="letter-spacing: inherit;"><p style="margin-bottom: -30px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;">1</p></div><p style="margin-left: 15px;padding-bottom: 24px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 20px;color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;font-weight: bold;"><strong style="letter-spacing: inherit;color: rgb(55, 80, 114);">iPad Pro 11/13寸</strong></p></div><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">关于新的 iPad Pro，消费者最容易感受到的就是苹果终于为iPad Pro搭载了 全新的OLED 屏幕。并且，与市面上常规 OLED 屏幕不同的是，这是一种名为 tOLED 的全新显示技术，与传统 OLED 屏幕相比， tOLED 通过双层结构设计能在保持高对比度和广色域的同时，进一步提升屏幕亮度和耐用性。</p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="327" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="100081044" data-ratio="0.5813333333333334" data-type="png" data-w="750" height="1128" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 100%;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto;" title="图源：苹果" width="1940" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBJptz9zWxHxcOPokqmxTT1Y6qZFrJUVULHQ0jutYrWNtEaZbbQ6Cz32XmcdsqDFAf0dIewjOaP5icg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"><figcaption style="margin-top: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">图源：苹果</figcaption></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">苹果将其命名为双层串联 OLED ，这块新屏幕让iPad Pro的全屏亮度来到了1000nit，峰值亮度来到了1600nit，同时在XDR显示器上的纳米纹玻璃也“下放”到了iPad Pro上，所有这一切为新 iPad Pro 构成了「超精视网膜XDR 」显示屏。</p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="320" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="100081042" data-ratio="0.5693333333333334" data-type="png" data-w="750" height="1282" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 100%;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto;" title="图源：苹果" width="2252" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBJptz9zWxHxcOPokqmxTT1Y6NRNATR7bDjYSic64rzpaqoMoxHNia8hPkIXh3meBFib3qicDYsljLCMYQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"><figcaption style="margin-top: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">图源：苹果</figcaption></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">同时，这也是 iPad Pro 11寸版本首次放弃 LCD 屏幕。一直以来用户都纷纷抱怨 iPad Pro 11寸从2018年发布到去年更新的M2版本，屏幕完全没有换过，终于苹果在这一代选择为11寸的 iPad Pro 更新了全新的屏幕。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">除去屏幕的升级，新的iPad Pro 还采用全新的 M4 芯片，跳过了在 Mac 上使用的 M3 。</p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="259" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="100081040" data-ratio="0.4613333333333333" data-type="jpeg" data-w="750" height="1179" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 100%;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto;" title="图源：苹果" width="2556" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jopKOlhibRBJptz9zWxHxcOPokqmxTT1YVzJ5MQ21tXGlC1q4OCag3U9ddx1vsiaKc1icF3jknStNxn4v9fWibFib6g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"><figcaption style="margin-top: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">图源：苹果</figcaption></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">全新的 M4 芯片基于全新的架构设计，可以说是一块专为 AI 性能推出的全新处理器。它拥有4个性能核心和6个能效核心，支持光线追踪和硬件加速功能，专业渲染性能相较于M2快4倍的同时，处理相同工作的能耗却只有M2的一半。</p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="280" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="100081045" data-ratio="0.49866666666666665" data-type="png" data-w="750" height="880" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 100%;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto;" title="图源：苹果" width="1766" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBJptz9zWxHxcOPokqmxTT1YQMDGB9J7OMPFwXqSbLO1SNj4PzSek4WiauFuI1c2IVHLNYFpIHGbmow/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"><figcaption style="margin-top: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">图源：苹果</figcaption></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">苹果宣称这枚全新的M4处理器拥有迄今为止最强大的神经网络引擎，能够达到每秒38万亿次运算速度。为了“压制住”这个性能野兽，新的iPad Pro在机身内部增加了散热组建，以便保持新 iPad Pro 为专业级用户提供更加稳定、持久的高性能运算。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">三维尺寸方面，iPad Pro 11寸的厚度为5.3mm，而13寸的iPad Pro厚度更加夸张，只有 5.1mm ，两者与iPad Air 一样，机身均为铝合金材质。<span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">&nbsp;</span></p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="494" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="100081048" data-ratio="0.8786666666666667" data-type="png" data-w="750" height="1224" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 100%;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto;" title="图源：苹果" width="1392" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBJptz9zWxHxcOPokqmxTT1YUQOP1icWIwZUWJrK0yBbTCHa0cpd1u2SLI7KGcia42AUWMUdUEibfpeAA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"><figcaption style="margin-top: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">图源：苹果</figcaption></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">其他配置方面，新款的iPad Pro 与Air一样将前置1200W摄像头移到了横屏的中间，方便配合妙控键盘时使用。iPhone上的原彩闪光灯也替代双色温闪光灯登陆 iPad Pro ，这让用户用 iPad Pro 直接拍摄、扫描纸质文件时可以获得更好的体验（这点真的不错）。</p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="553" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="100081049" data-ratio="0.984" data-type="png" data-w="750" height="870" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 100%;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto;" title="图源：苹果" width="884" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBJptz9zWxHxcOPokqmxTT1YiaRfGSEH5dQZXNLySR1N61LpLib7ucZshrBBcr0JcMsQHUWib0s33bbSw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"><figcaption style="margin-top: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">图源：苹果</figcaption></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">软件层面，伴随着新的iPad Pro，苹果为专业级用户带来了全新的 Final Cut Pro 和Logic Pro 2 ，相信在新的一年，iPad Pro的生产力功能会更多“亿点点”。<span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">新的 iPad Pro 起售容量为256GB，拥有256G、512G、1TB、2TB四个容量版本。11寸的售价分别为8999、10699、14099、17499元。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">注意，1TB和2TB版本可以额外多花800元选购可以减少眩光的「纳米纹理玻璃」。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">5G蜂窝版本在此售价的基础上再增加1700元。</span></p><div style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div style="letter-spacing: inherit;"><p style="margin-bottom: -30px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;">1</p></div><p style="margin-left: 15px;padding-bottom: 24px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 20px;color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;font-weight: bold;"><strong style="letter-spacing: inherit;color: rgb(55, 80, 114);">Apple Pencil Pro</strong></p></div><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">为了给绘画用户带来更好的体验，苹果在今晚配合新iPad 推出了全新的Apple Pencil Pro，外观和Apple Pencil 2代并无明显区别，但它在机身内塞入了一个全新的传感器，支持了轻捏功能，配合悬浮定位可以让用户在不接触屏幕的情况下完成菜单选取、图层选择等操作。</p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="366" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="100081047" data-ratio="0.652" data-type="png" data-w="750" height="1570" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 100%;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto;" title="图源：苹果" width="2410" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBJptz9zWxHxcOPokqmxTT1YnIQXF4R4Gfg87icIPBow1ibCUgPpBLYqQVw6pdFzTZIBND095UiaAgwMg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"><figcaption style="margin-top: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">图源：苹果</figcaption></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">与此同时，Apple Pencil Pro 还支持了「侧旋功能」，它可以让用户在旋转笔身调整画笔的笔触角度，从而画出更加拟真的绘画效果。触觉反馈的加入，能让用户更加真实的确认自己是否选中图层或功能，避免误操作的发生。</p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="324" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="100081046" data-ratio="0.576" data-type="png" data-w="750" height="1216" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 100%;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto;" title="图源：苹果" width="2110" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBJptz9zWxHxcOPokqmxTT1YGT7KF4UfjzroQbmUdoC83SlwGtiagpH1ric0JOtthfibWSMiaJ2IiaqzywQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"><figcaption style="margin-top: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">图源：苹果</figcaption></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">新款Apple Pencil Pro不仅支持搭载 M4 芯片的iPad Pro ，同时还支持现有的 M2 芯片的 iPad Pro 以及 iPad Air，国行售价为999元。</p><div style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div style="letter-spacing: inherit;"><p style="margin-bottom: -30px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;">1</p></div><p style="margin-left: 15px;padding-bottom: 24px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 20px;color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;font-weight: bold;"><strong style="letter-spacing: inherit;color: rgb(55, 80, 114);">妙控键盘</strong></p></div><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">配合全新的 iPad Pro，被专业用户诟病太重、缺乏功能键的妙控键盘也在今晚迎来了更新。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">全新打造的妙控键盘采用了铝合金掌托和触控板，并且终于加入了功能键区，苹果没有对外公布新款妙控键盘的具体重量，但官方表示会比老款更加轻便。</p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="328" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="100081051" data-ratio="0.584" data-type="png" data-w="750" height="1318" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 100%;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto;" title="图源：苹果" width="2258" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBJptz9zWxHxcOPokqmxTT1YbXmK6OhVpkQfqg7lY0jbyLhspF7FRJC43ibt4dpn408dsLxJcNahVicA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"><figcaption style="margin-top: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">图源：苹果</figcaption></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">新键盘同样拥有黑白两个颜色，售价2799元，仅支持 M4 芯片的iPad Pro。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">以上就是今晚时常仅有<span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">35</span>分钟的，<span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">iPad&nbsp;</span>发布会内容汇总，我们会在上手新设备后第一时间为大家带来详细评测，至于用户关心的的<span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">&nbsp;AI&nbsp;</span>特性，让我们在<span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">6</span>月即将到来的<span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">WWDC 2024&nbsp;</span>不见不散。<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="187" data-backw="562" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100053895" data-ratio="0.3333333333333333" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="900" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBJ9EQTbUZzia1Qh8forjSicACQEria1n77KGakaqc8jBtYIdwv8tdqSyhLDdd8KlQINjicZSkPKfPl83Q/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100081052" data-ratio="0.05555555555555555" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBIICkpD4bwucu7E3vVbBsQJ2ZN4cLvfH3jVhWmIhdXUdSYQ8Scf77QCGmGjmaSN5D4aHU4JqKnRSA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: right;"><a target="_blank" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNjU2ODM2NQ==&amp;mid=2247564687&amp;idx=1&am