        <title type="html"><![CDATA[别吹ChatGPT和Claude了，最适合小白的写作AI还得靠国产｜AI 横评]]></title>
        <id>2247564535_1</id>
        <link href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNjU2ODM2NQ==&amp;mid=2247564535&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=99973e07d0d457be28fa4eed3a41d1dd&amp;chksm=c236e635f5416f2396aad3aeb0557256aa5e918784694da98fbb4ec68a8da59cd0f5a7c5728d#rd"/>
        <updated>2024-05-05T01:59:28.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;" data-mpa-powered-by="yiban.io"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="562" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="100080752" data-ratio="1" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jopKOlhibRBIJ0u47KX0VotIfjGKQRbx9YXPj6ia1rx32I21dCDmdW6sSkLQ5cvAPfEIr0lAWz2PKkQUKue3EIZw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"><span style="font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;"></span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;">作者｜丸丸柚贝<br style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;">邮箱｜wangxianxian@pingwest.com&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;">编辑｜椰子<br style="letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;text-align: start;">邮箱｜</span><span style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;">lixiaoxian</span><span style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;">@pingwest.com&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;padding: 0px 0.5em;margin-bottom: 24px;"><span style="text-indent: 0em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 12px;font-family: UICTFontTextStyleEmphasizedBody;font-weight: bold;letter-spacing: normal;"></span></p><p style="text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;padding: 0px 0.5em;margin-bottom: 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: UICTFontTextStyleEmphasizedBody;font-size: 12px;font-weight: bold;letter-spacing: normal;text-indent: 0em;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">身为文案内容创作的打工人，每天都要不停的码字，写文案，写脚本，写日报，写周报等等等。。。<span style="color: rgb(0, 128, 255);"><strong>脑细胞真的剩的不多了！</strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">所以，如果这些事都能交给 AI 来做，那等于我直接可以带薪躺平了。直接什么文案、脚本、论文、作文、日报、周报，多浪费一根头发都是对 AI 的不尊重。</p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;padding: 0px 0.5em;margin-bottom: 24px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="236" data-backw="236" data-height="236" data-imgfileid="100019357" data-ratio="1" data-type="png" data-w="236" data-width="236" style="width: 322px;height: 322px;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: rgb(180, 180, 180) 0em 0em 0.5em 0px;font-size: 17px;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7TvynHBHPfavrx7FonqpU5Em4JfqX8ibJD3LlhV1N40y9ulyHmZPJicAlU8P8G28U7mzpLuSFs9WGCg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">目前大家认可能力比较强的AI无非就是Open AI的ChatGPT、Anthropic的Claude、Google的Gemini等等。。。。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">但对于小白来说，这些工具用起来，<span style="color: rgb(0, 128, 255);"><strong>真的是一步一个坎</strong></span>。而且现阶段国内模型理解和处理汉语任务的能力还是强一些。</p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;padding: 0px 0.5em;margin-bottom: 24px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="234" data-backw="238" data-height="234" data-imgfileid="100019358" data-ratio="0.9831932773109243" data-type="png" data-w="238" data-width="238" style="width: 320px;height: 315px;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: rgb(180, 180, 180) 0em 0em 0.5em 0px;font-size: 17px;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7TvynHBHPfavrx7FonqpU5EpcpEws4wQjY3hcEwgPVqla6ebWakgQ7RyGCTgUVfmruEQj1ib77U15g/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">话不多说，直接上干货吧还是！今天就先拉出来两个目前国内比较火热的AI写作产品——<span style="color: rgb(0, 128, 255);"><strong>秘塔写作猫</strong></span>和<span style="color: rgb(0, 128, 255);"><strong>蛙蛙写作</strong></span>，深度测评对比一下，到底哪个才是最适合小白写作的。</p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="51" data-backw="56" data-height="84" data-imgfileid="100019355" data-ratio="0.9130434782608695" data-type="png" data-w="92" data-width="92" style="width: 59px;height: 54px;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7TvynHBHPfavrx7FonqpU5EKSRHztkG00wROqCLwODRDoocASjRJGNAtxFXkWdgl8cHdYpqx2K2Vw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="56" data-backw="56" data-height="910" data-imgfileid="100019359" data-ratio="1" data-type="jpeg" data-w="910" data-width="910" style="font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;width: 50px;height: 50px;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5gR6KWHNb7TvynHBHPfavrx7FonqpU5E0XqRqhKgDd7SLXzdjeOibJFRVVBWJK6QZ0yWrj9IiaPxKBeRzaVQib30A/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="52" data-backw="60" data-height="52" data-imgfileid="100019502" data-ratio="0.8666666666666667" data-type="png" data-w="60" data-width="64" height="52" style="font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;width: 62px;height: 54px;" width="60" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/TC6SuYvaia9sNIAxx0q65ZSeVeIOK22AJhXxyF6jrHruicwRJJdlY64RAQn35PuzV4PLQFstxL17ql2O2ibXIxTIA/640?&amp;wx_fmt=png"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: justify;"></span></p><div style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div style="letter-spacing: inherit;"><p style="margin-bottom: -30px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;">1</p></div><p style="margin-left: 15px;padding-bottom: 24px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 20px;color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;font-weight: bold;"><strong style="letter-spacing: inherit;color: rgb(55, 80, 114);">自媒体创作者必选它！</strong></p></div><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">内容创作者真的很需要有网感的文字或者视频展现方式进行创作才能吸引到大家，这大概就是大家说的<span style="color: rgb(0, 128, 255);"><strong>流量密码</strong></span>吧！但是AI真的懂人类，了解什么是流量密码吗？行不行的上案例吧👇</p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;padding: 0px 0.5em;margin-bottom: 24px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="327" data-backw="426" data-height="1070" data-imgfileid="100019363" data-ratio="0.7675925925925926" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1394" style="width: 418px;height: 321px;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: rgb(180, 180, 180) 0em 0em 0.5em 0px;font-size: 17px;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7TvynHBHPfavrx7FonqpU5Eq67yQkSs6Igu2lo60TC2e2U06jaoxrHrC1n116wTxPibS0t2ZfIXMug/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: justify;"></span></p><div style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div style="letter-spacing: inherit;"><p style="margin-bottom: -30px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;">1</p></div><p style="margin-left: 15px;padding-bottom: 24px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 20px;color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;font-weight: bold;"><strong style="letter-spacing: inherit;color: rgb(55, 80, 114);">小红书文案</strong></p></div><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">小红书种草文案，不如它俩王婆卖瓜，自卖自夸一下吧🫣。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">👉秘塔写作猫：<span style="color: rgb(0, 128, 255);"><strong>标明产品描述的要求</strong></span>，文案比较有真实性，种草感比较强，自带标签，不满意还可以一键多次生成；但是有时生成的内容与事实有偏差。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">另外，<span style="color: rgb(0, 128, 255);"><strong>秘塔写作猫</strong></span>对于各种使用场景还支持<span style="color: rgb(0, 128, 255);"><strong>批量生成</strong></span>（这里以小红书文案为例），而且生成的效果也不错，这个确实大大的提高了工作效率了！</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">👉蛙蛙写作：文案标题中自动添加符合的表情，与目标平台的风格相符，可以联网查询相关资料，降低出错率；但是文案内容有点官方，广告感较强，没太有种草感。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">这一局<span style="color: rgb(0, 128, 255);"><strong>秘塔写作猫胜出</strong></span>🏆</p><table><tbody><tr><td width="260" valign="middle" style="word-break: break-all;" align="center"><p style="padding: 0px 0.5em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="444" data-backw="239" data-height="3814" data-imgfileid="100019410" data-ratio="1.8583333333333334" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="2052" style=