        <title type="html"><![CDATA[光靠流量，造不好中国车？]]></title>
        <id>2247564525_1</id>
        <link href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNjU2ODM2NQ==&amp;mid=2247564525&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=17c95182d414f66a8a37a221431c5bf6&amp;chksm=c236e62ff5416f3999b897e9d7d9d7be191ee100231747f2e72991607cc1fa73f66331f52513#rd"/>
        <updated>2024-05-04T01:57:26.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;" data-mpa-powered-by="yiban.io"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="562" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="100080868" data-ratio="1" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jopKOlhibRBJ9aTJ8mW1kzHd1MBXiaiagFbNtV6HhcXpicOQOiaLu3b7Et6bDVHlAPBCXBxb9s4JHIK5gOia3gGTK3xw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"></p><div style="margin-bottom: 30px;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-image: none;background-position: initial;background-size: initial;background-repeat: initial;background-attachment: initial;background-origin: initial;background-clip: initial;"><p style="padding-top: 15px;letter-spacing: inherit;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);font-size: 13px;line-height: 21px;">作者<span style="letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(221, 221, 221);">｜</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">董楠</span><br style="letter-spacing: inherit;">邮箱<span style="letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(221, 221, 221);">｜</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">dongnan@pingwest.com</span></p></div><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">近日，“车圈网红”周鸿祎披露了迈巴赫事件的新进展：他表示二手车辆的拍卖尾款已经收到，下周开始开始试驾各家车厂送来的新车。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">在二手车行当折腾了数天之后，他似乎也想尽快给这件事画上一个句号。这也让这个霸占了车圈数天流量的事件终于迎来了阶段性的尾声。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">最近，互联网流量一直围绕在车圈：北京国际车展正在举办，车圈大佬都参与其中，而互联网大佬们则以各种各样的姿势掀翻了车圈的屋顶。就连周鸿祎这样的半个圈外人也保持了旺盛的“战斗欲”。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">不过终归有人憋不住，说出了真心话。最近在一场直播中，罗永浩对北京车展上</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">CEO</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">们的互动开启了吐槽，他直言“看不懂，感觉很怪。”</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">对于老总们在车展上互相“串门儿”，罗永浩直呼，</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">“有很多竞争对手假模假式的，他们可能乐在其中，我看着有点怪怪的啊。”罗永浩对大佬相互串门进行了点评：“还有A厂商跑到B厂商那仔细打量尬聊，画风挺怪的。”</span></p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="770" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="100080859" data-ratio="1.3693333333333333" data-type="jpeg" data-w="750" height="1615" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 100%;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto;" title="图源：罗永浩视频截图" width="1179" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jopKOlhibRBJ9aTJ8mW1kzHd1MBXiaiagFbDCoQ9JYMYSRAJqEmpRLW7qHP4m03rhNAiaYHGMS9ib9eVaZTqPDbBIIw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"><figcaption style="margin-top: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">图源：罗永浩视频截图</figcaption></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">罗永浩纳闷的是，</span><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">明明是竞争对手，为什么要表演一团和气？</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">确实，在本届北京车展前，</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">CEO</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">们，尤其是传统车企的领导们，几乎是不互动的。不过例行的去其他家转转，倒一直是车企领导的必修课，毕竟，车展是直观了解竞争对手的最好机会。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">一般来说，最常见的是“皮尺部”小分队，趴在车底研究各家新车。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">这届北京车展上有点不一样。比亚迪董事长王传福坐在小米</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">SU</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">7内，听雷军介绍新车；魏建军给宝马董事长齐普策介绍坦克700，车展第三天，魏建军还在车展上逛了丰田，试了普拉多；</span></p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="375" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="100080858" data-ratio="0.6666666666666666" data-type="jpeg" data-w="690" height="460" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 100%;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto;" title="魏建军与齐普策 图源：网路" width="690" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jopKOlhibRBJ9aTJ8mW1kzHd1MBXiaiagFbCOcKQIVAicKLXh6cRsJqYS8FibD5vTM2J43TXcCWwNTBKJTS2z5JkSOQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"><figcaption style="margin-top: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">魏建军与齐普策 图源：网路</figcaption></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">车展第二天，奇瑞董事长尹同跃在展台上与搜狐创始人张朝阳一起讲起了物理课；</span></p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font