ng: inherit;">还发了一条北京车展一日</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">V</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">log……</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">媒体日上，还有不少外国人出现，包括车企工程师、媒体，以及外国经销商，据说这也是往届北京车展上很难见到的，甚至一些外国人直接在现场直播讲车，看起来十分热闹。</span></p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="422" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="100080857" data-ratio="0.7506666666666667" data-type="jpeg" data-w="750" height="4284" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 100%;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto;" title="外国媒体现场讲解中国品牌汽车 图源：品驾 摄" width="5712" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jopKOlhibRBJ9aTJ8mW1kzHd1MBXiaiagFbiblx6aejO9ia6GOyBgiagZatTWUYuP2yT2yhHJHibeLBSgwPM2A6QeTadQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"><figcaption style="margin-top: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">外国媒体现场讲解中国品牌汽车 图源：品驾 摄</figcaption></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;text-decoration:underline;">为什么车企老板们成为了流量担当？当网红跟造车真的有必然联系吗？</span></span></span></span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;text-decoration:underline;"><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">外国人扎堆欣赏中国车，说明了什么？</span></span></span></span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">首先，今年车企老板、</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">CEO</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">们的抛头露脸，与雷军的流量辐射不无相关，很多品牌甚至为老板亲自直播、拍视频做了不少准备，可以说，一切镜头都在计划内。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">从车模时代、请明星代言，到老板亲自代言，这其实也是最近十年来车展的一个不小变化。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">就在车展前，尹同跃、魏建军就已经开始出现在直播中，为自家技术、车型带货。魏建军在直播中曾提到，“目前市场很激烈，大家都很焦虑。”</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">尹同跃也在直播中谈到，亲自上阵也是利用新的互联网思维，向余承东学习、向雷军学习，怎么样亲自去讲解去介绍产品。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">就如同大家都再说今年的车市卷，<span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">一方面，想获得可观的增长越来越难，另一方面，中国品牌崛起，好的产品、好的技术越来越多，这无疑加剧了竞争</span>。老板亲自带货，其实就是为自家产品代言。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">本届北京车展颇为高调的还有宁德时代董事长曾毓群，在不少直播中，都有曾毓群与车企老板们的同框画面。宁德时代在本届北京车展发布的神行PLUS超充电池，目的也是用超充生态与</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">C</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">端用户建立直接认知。</span></p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="715" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="100080860" data-ratio="1.272" data-type="png" data-w="750" height="1308" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 100%;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto;" title="互联网大佬周鸿祎也跨圈成为了车圈网红，图源：网络" width="1028" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBJ9aTJ8mW1kzHd1MBXiaiagFbK3duz1Q1Libia89aSdzHFIsYjHmc4WbmJPDPRoxFOsx5s4V6yvt0QXCg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"><figcaption style="margin-top: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">互联网大佬周鸿祎也跨圈成为了车圈网红，图源：网络</figcaption></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">当然，关于要不要搞直播，很多车企老总也有自己的看法。长安汽车董事长朱华荣说，长安要培养自己的雷布斯和余大嘴。最近，深蓝汽车</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">CEO</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">邓承浩就在视频号上做起了新能源汽车科普。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">极氪CEO安聪慧则表示，作为</span><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">CEO，</span><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">时间精力有限，放在产品、技术、业务上更重要</span>。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">毫无疑问，<span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">本届北京车展，国内车企正式开启了“流量时代”，企业家网红化更容易拉近汽车品牌与用户的距离。</span>而车企老总之间在车展上互带流量，弱化了商业竞争的味道，让很多人觉得不适，因为它看起来并不像汽车行业竞争的常态。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">但是从中国品牌发展新能源汽车的大形势来看，中国品牌新能源汽车已经成为一张名片，在北京车展上，利用流量形成自己的名片，并带动很多外资大佬跟风，这种趋势本身并不是坏事。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">当然，是否需要流量带货，如何解开流量密码，对于汽车企业来说，其实是一道非常大的难题。理想汽车产品线总裁刘杰就说，</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">造车新势力卷流量卷不过手机企业</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">，</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">因此在流量竞争面前，有的车企找到了新思路，有的车企也在避免流量竞争带来的战略失焦。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">很多车企在北京车展上也是展示“顺势而为”的功力，借雷军的人气，引流到自家展台，仅仅是汽车行业进入流量时代的第一步。老板们勇敢地走到了台前，但是谁真正强化了自家品牌，还有待时间验证。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">另一方面，由于本届车展的流量效应，也多多少少将本该在车展上被放大的新车、新技术，因为过高的流量而被遮盖了。即便老板亲自带货，如何做到长期、有效的向用户传递品牌、产品、技术价值，只靠流量或许是不够的，与用户建立有效的沟通机制，更为重要。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">很多人其实已经发现，北京车展上的外国人比往届多了，他们都在围观中国品牌汽车，这种变化，恰恰印证了中国技术的魅力。</span></p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="316" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="100080862" data-ratio="0.5621212121212121" data-type="jpeg" data-w="660" height="371" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 100%;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto;" title="图源：网络" width="660" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jopKOlhibRBJ9aTJ8mW1kzHd1MBXiaiagFbtH31bZADE6UofKHSdJKUxoyTrdXya6p6pbRKpxcgP74nrb6A6iaSSDQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"><figcaption style="margin-top: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">图源：网络</figcaption></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">有外国工程师在观察、测量中国品牌汽车，有外国媒体、车企员工在围观小米汽车发布会，还有海外经销商现场订车，很多人都感叹，本届车展是外国人最多的一次，让北京车展作为国际</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">A</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">展的含金量更高了，也证明中国汽车在全球的影响力。</span></p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="375" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="100080861" data-ratio="0.6666666666666666" data-type="jpeg" data-w="690" height="460" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 100%;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto;" title="图源：网络" width="690" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jopKOlhibRBJ9aTJ8mW1kzHd1MBXiaiagFbhA0STZQFTR56t83woPx7WSNOaKmLd0LaLMGpl9mYdQ7wKA2TMb8bmA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"><figcaption style="margin-top: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">图源：网络</figcaption></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">这其实是本届北京车展上一个重大的转折。事实上，近两年，国际大型车展都有走弱的趋势。一方面，受到国际市场环境影响，很多国际品牌参加车展的意愿越来越低；另一方面，汽车行业真正的转型在中国，这也让包括国际品牌、中国品牌在内的全球汽车品牌，愿意在中国分享最新的技术，并在中国首发全球车型，并增强在中国投资的意愿。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">所以说，进入流量时代，是中国汽车渴望品牌影响力的一个阶段。但中国汽车真正在全球的影响力，当然不是仅仅靠流量就够的。技术、产品，以及技术创新下的良性竞争，才能带来真正有影响力的中国车。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: right;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><a target="_blank" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNjU2ODM2NQ==&amp;mid=2247564503&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=f2c7ca2c4f393f6f4e9254bc9120737f&amp;chksm=c236e615f5416f039e450005d6ac7fccaef5234b5f56d217c443cd23fa8ec4bea3a3ed2fddce&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" textvalue="‍‍" linktype="text" imgurl="" imgdata="null" data-itemshowtype="0" tab="innerlink" data-linktype="1"><span class="js_jump_icon h5_image_link" style="width: 100%;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="143" data-backw="562" data-cropselx1="0" data-cropselx2="562" data-cropsely1="0" data-cropsely2="143" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100080864" data-ratio="0.2544444444444444" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="900" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBJ9aTJ8mW1kzHd1MBXiaiagFbXkJq6V2geKyhBHB6OIe9jgicUjfg8ecBTmicTzo0nKWJj84pibnUfP0CQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></span></a><a target="_blank" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNjU2ODM2NQ==&amp;mid=2247564398&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=7ab0fe41b385be332aabc3543f574585&amp;chksm=c236e6acf5416fba7473494b146d7890435842de0e2daab94f952326c222b5a45c33e5e46105&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" textvalue="‍‍" linktype="text" imgurl="" imgdata="null" data-itemshowtype="0" tab="innerlink" data-linktype="1"><span class="js_jump_icon h5_image_link" style="width: 100%;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="143" data-backw="562" data-cropselx1="0" data-cropselx2="562" data-cropsely1="0" data-cropsely2="143" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100080865" data-ratio="0.2544444444444444" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="900" style="outline: 0px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBIJ0u47KX0VotIfjGKQRbx91BicaULXdOA4ibY2azdGMcdPVSiaJcnaaTFCGd0kkRbGV8n8oicdObicBug/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></span></a><a target="_blank" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNjU2ODM2NQ==&amp;mid=2247564294&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=e831c8f860d02dad329389778640c7f5&amp;chksm=c236e6c4f5416fd2bdec7d99c155e97f151cc5b7a34fae15fa2889754461cdfb90fc6bd16db9&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" textvalue="‍‍" linktype="text" imgurl="" imgdata="null" data-itemshowtype="0" tab="innerlink" data-linktype="1"><span class="js_jump_icon h5_image_link" style="width: 100%;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="143" data-backw="562" data-cropselx1="0" data-cropselx2="562" data-cropsely1="0" data-cropsely2="143" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100080866" data-ratio="0.2544444444444444" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="900" style="outline: 0px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBK93Y1z1PKicD0APkibZznlEUkUvd6acChIO9KIsr4iahkAQMuBtPAVuVhKo8icqv2OJZGshJM4iabU22A/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></span></a><span style="text-wrap: wrap;text-align: right;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline: 0px;color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-size: 14px;font-family: PingFangSC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;">点个</span><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);text-align: right;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline: 0px;color: rgb(32, 75, 169);"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: PingFangSC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;">“</span><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.578px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;">在看</span></strong><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: PingFangSC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;">”</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);text-align: right;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-size: 14px;font-family: PingFangSC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;">，再走吧</span><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">👀</span></span></p><p><br></p><a href="https://www.pingwest.com/a/294682">阅读原文</a>]]></summary>
