;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div style="letter-spacing: inherit;"><p style="margin-bottom: -30px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;">1</p></div><p style="margin-left: 15px;padding-bottom: 24px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 20px;color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;font-weight: bold;"><strong style="letter-spacing: inherit;color: rgb(55, 80, 114);">云厂商等大混战：以AI之名</strong></p></div><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">除了智谱AI之外，主打“大模型”的广告主里，我们也遇到了华为盘古大模型。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">同样的，它展示了自己的客户案例。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="422" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="100080249" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBLjsT71yUC46kRe4dan1D3JniaKia4ZRjTic172LicJg5XuFDuDISbr0qLibchbWZhibPS0lPgu6SpjxLBw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">这个推广盘古大模型的广告其实是华为云的。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">在大模型的浪潮里，目前最佳的售卖方式其实是在卖云计算。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">而云厂商们也以AI之名，再度加强了广告大战的投入。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">杭州机场是个最有代表性的混战之处。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">你能看到阿里云最新的一批代言人。</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">打头阵的，是大模型公司百川智能的创始人王小川。</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="412" data-backw="552" data-imgfileid="100080246" data-ratio="0.7472353870458136" data-type="png" data-w="633" height="413.010009765625" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" width="552.010009765625" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBLjsT71yUC46kRe4dan1D3JkTKYxdTfxjs3OZofg2vfkVaiaGR5eePjArZrOtwRMtRg28e4fWF9gjQ/640?wx_fmt=png"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;">（杭州萧山机场实拍）</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">然后就遇到华为云在阿里云老家打的广告。&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><o:page></o:page></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="422" data-backw="562" data-cropselx1="0" data-cropselx2="562" data-cropsely1="0" data-cropsely2="421" data-imgfileid="100080245" data-ratio="0.75" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jopKOlhibRBI2QiaWVCcvzGJwgwSpncBC9Nicu27zCzt741mYW7jyxg1IW6yHJOdh5E28FUVgGIWnJEX9HMnveBmg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;M